Title: arrayReverseFill(func, arr1, ...)
Description: Scan through arr1 from the last element to the first element and replace arr1[i] by arr1[i + 1] if func(arr1[i], ..., arrN[i]) returns 0. The last element of arr1 will not be replaced.
Examples: SELECT arrayReverseFill(x -> not isNull(x), [1, null, 3, 11, 12, null, null, 5, 6, 14, null, null]) AS res
